<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Transport:-</span></strong></p>
<p>The college has four vehicles. The bus plies for Day boarders and for the students educational/Industrial visits. The students also visit historical places by making use of Institute bus. As the Institute is located on the NH-21 and is most approachable from all nearby areas.</p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sport</span></strong><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">s:-</span></strong></p>
