<p>SIRDA Group of Institutes believes, education without activities is always incomplete. So games and sports are necessary part of education. Extra-curricular activities empower students to make their own active decisions and also help them to gain an accurate experience, skills and confidence to lead them on the path of their future. Moreover, participating in games and sports is very beneficial in developing and understanding one’s personality type. It is considered by the SIRDA Group of Institutes that through participation in sports and different games, students learn cooperation, teamwork, leadership methods and time management. Games also help by discovering their hidden talent, help them to interact with different people and make them learn about many things outside their own environment. In essence, games affect a person’s psychological state of mind which leads to excitement and brings out the feeling of one being proud for accomplishments. Sports and games give encouragement to face all the hard challenges of life. SIRDA College has planned the Time Table in such a manner that studies and games are balanced for developing outer and inner personality of students.</p>
<p>SIRDA Group of Institutions has Sports Club where the concerned committee organizes sports activities such as annual sports meet, as well as different games and tournaments which are held throughout the year on a regular basis. Various indoor and outdoor games are available such as:</p>
<p><strong>Badminton, Volleyball, Basketball, Kabaddi, Athletics, Table Tennis, Weight Lifting, Power Lifting, Gym, Carom board and Chess etc.</strong></p>
